505
00:32:11,238 --> 00:32:13,219
Ti pesiamo e dovresti aver preso un chilo.

506
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:14,780
Te lo ricordi?

507
00:32:15,780 --> 00:32:16,362
Sì, certo.

508
00:32:19,503 --> 00:32:23,788
