00:42:00,471 --> 00:42:00,670
Sì.

644
00:42:01,012 --> 00:42:02,914
Ti devo portare qualcosa?

645
00:42:03,414 --> 00:42:04,074
No, ce la faccio.

646
00:42:32,931 --> 00:42:33,913
Davide!

